   321	  2. Constructs either `SqliteStore.open(...)` or
   322	     `InMemoryStore(...)` based on `--db-path`.
   323	  3. Calls `eden_wire.server.make_app(store)`.
   324	  4. Runs it via `uvicorn`.
   325	
   326	  Logs structured events (stdout) for observability.
   327	
   328	- **`reference/services/orchestrator-service/`** — Entry point
   329	  `eden_orchestrator.__main__` that:
   330	  1. Parses CLI args (`--task-store-url`, `--experiment-id`,
   331	     `--repo-path`, `--plan-tasks`, `--implement-task-prefix`,
   332	     `--evaluate-task-prefix`).
   333	  2. Constructs `StoreClient(base_url, experiment_id)`.
   334	  3. Constructs scripted workers (Phase 5 / 8a flavor) against the
   335	     `StoreClient`.
   336	  4. Constructs an `Integrator(store=client, repo=..., author=...)`;
   337	     passes `integrator.integrate` as `integrate_trial`.
   338	  5. Calls `run_experiment(...)` to completion.
   339	  6. Exits zero on clean termination.
